{"article_id":"OsCbdsSyIlBaEEP2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Amid growing Democratic accusations","depth":10},{"id":1,"text":"of overreaching , especially on the matter of Hillary Clinton ' s emails ,","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"Republicans on the House Benghazi Committee are now reconsidering how aggressively to pursue the email scandal","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"that ' s been dogging the Democratic front-runner .","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"The committee is also undecided about whether to call ex-Clinton campaign staffer Heather Samuelson ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"who helped screen Clinton ' s State Department emails ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"according to a GOP source .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Just a few weeks ago , GOP members of the panel were eager to question Samuelson ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"because","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"panel sources say","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"she was the lawyer","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"who initially chose","depth":14},{"id":12,"text":"which of Clinton ' s emails were work-related","depth":15},{"id":13,"text":"- and thus should be turned over to the State Department -","depth":15},{"id":14,"text":"and which would ultimately get deleted .","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"Now , however , Republicans are debating whether to bring her in .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"\" The question becomes :","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Is it worth the hassle and the drama ? \"","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"the GOP source said .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"The reevaluation follows a Thursday hearing","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"which was widely seen as a success for Clinton ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"while Republicans failed to strike any decisive blows .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Meanwhile , Democrats amped up their claims","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that the entire investigation was a partisan witch hunt .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"The panel ' s mandate was to investigate the circumstances","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"surrounding the killing of four Americans outside the U.S. consulate in Benghazi , Libya , in 2012 , in the waning months of Clinton ' s tenure as secretary of state .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"But after the revelation","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that Clinton used a private email server for her State Department correspondence ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Republicans on the panel began probing further into whether she had turned over all relevant emails .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Still , GOP leaders maintained","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that they ' ve never focused directly on Clinton 's email setup ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"which is currently being investigated by the FBI ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"although a fired GOP committee staffer said","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"they zeroed in on the issue","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"after the server was discovered .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Faced with a growing barrage of Democratic accusations","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that they ' re targeting Clinton for political reasons ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Republicans on the panel are downplaying the email question","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"- at least for now .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"After their high-profile turn in the national spotlight with Clinton ' s Thursday testimony , the panel is headed back behind closed-doors for purely Benghazi-related interviews with officials from the White House , the Department of Defense and CIA ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"sources said .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Committee Chairman Trey Gowdy","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"( R-S.C. )","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"has long maintained","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"he ' s only interested in the emails","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"because he wants to assemble a complete record of Clinton ' s communications","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"when she ran the State Department .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"During their investigation , Benghazi Republicans found about 15 Clinton emails","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that she never turned over","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"- raising GOP suspicions","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that more might be missing .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"But the email issue only came up briefly at the tail end of her marathon Benghazi hearing .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"And Republicans spent the bulk of their time","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"pressing Clinton over the security failures at the Libyan diplomatic mission ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and attacked her leadership of the State Department .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Still , even Gowdy admitted","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Clinton ' s 11-hour testimony failed to produce any major new revelations .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"\" I don ' t know","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that she testified that much different today","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"than she has previous times , \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"he told reporters after the hearing Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Republicans say","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"Clinton ' s testimony wasn ' t about scoring points","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"or catching her in a \" gotcha \" moment over the Benghazi attacks - or the emails issue , for that matter .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"They said","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"they were aiming to piece together a larger mosaic around the Sept. 11 , 2012 terrorist attack","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"that left four Americans dead .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"But after a lengthy day of tense , and sometimes confrontational testimony , Democrats aren ' t buying it .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"the American people are left wondering what prompted the select committee at all ;","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"there is not a single new ray of light","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"shed on the tragedy","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that took place years ago , \"","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"said Sen. Chuck Schumer","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"( D-N.Y. )","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"on a telephone call with reporters Friday .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"\" The committee Republicans badgered Hillary Clinton at every turn ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"they interrupted her","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"and threw the kitchen sink at her .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"despite all of the attacks","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Hillary was rock solid . \"","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Panel Republicans and Democrats took to the TV cameras Friday","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"to try to spin the hearing ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"with the left repeating their calls for the panel to disband ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"and the right insisting","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Clinton had been evasive .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Rep. Jim Jordan","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"( R-Ohio )","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"during a CNN appearance touted a series of new emails","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"he questioned Clinton about ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"which show","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"that she told her daughter , Chelsea , and the Egyptian prime minister","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"that the attacks were pre-meditated","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"- a statement","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"that contrasted with what U.S . Ambassador Susan Rice would say on TV shortly after the assault .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"He also defended Gowdy ' s comment","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that suggested","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Clinton had broken no new ground in her testimony .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"\" Of course she gave the same answer ;","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"she stuck to her story , \"","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"\" That ... is not that surprising . \"","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"Jordan , a dogged Oversight panel member with a reputation for rapid-fire questions , was the only Republican","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"who really took Clinton to task on the email issue Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"During the last round of questions , he pressed Clinton on why she would say","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"she was being \" as transparent as possible \"","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"when it took numerous lawsuits and demands from the committee","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"before she turned over her documents .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Clinton did not offer a direct answer for many of Jordan 's questions ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"including why she had given different dates for when she started using her private email","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"and why she suggested","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"the Secret Server protected her server .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"\" Secretary Clinton , seems like there 's a pattern , pattern","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"of changing your story , \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Jordan said .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"\" [ Y ] ou say one thing ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"the truth comes out ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"weeks and months later , you say something else . \"","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Clinton said","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"the panel should talk to her attorneys about those specifics .","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"And that was that .","depth":6},{"id":122,"text":"The committee spent less than 20 minutes on the matter in the 11 hour hearing .","depth":3},{"id":123,"text":"Committee spokesman Jamal Ware said","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"the panel will spend the next few weeks interviewing \" two individuals","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"whose identities must remain secret , \"","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"adding to more than 50 of about 70","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"they ' ve already completed .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"In the meantime , the committee might not say much about Clinton for a while , at least until the panel ' s final report .","depth":4},{"id":129,"text":"\" She ' s an important witness ,","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"you can ' t investigate Benghazi","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"without talking to the secretary of state at the relevant time ,","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"but","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"as I said this morning ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"she is one important witness out of 50 , \"","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Gowdy said","depth":5},{"id":136,"text":"shortly after the hearing ended on Thursday night .","depth":4},{"id":137,"text":"\" In terms of conclusions","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"drawn ,","depth":6},{"id":139,"text":"I don ' t draw conclusions until the end... .","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"We ' ll keep going on","depth":5},{"id":141,"text":"until we ' re able to interview all the witnesses","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"that we think","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"have access to relevant information . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":287,"left":265,"right":286,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":204,"right":264,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":178,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":167,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":165,"right":166,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":162,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":150,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":147,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":148,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":1